setPermitedVirtualDatacenters

public void setPermitedVirtualDatacenters(List<VirtualDatacenter> vdcs)
Limits user access ONLY to the virtual datacenters in the list. If the list is empty, user will get access to all virtual datacenters.

Parameters:
vdc - List of virtual datancers from the user's enterprise.
